</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Before you begin</title><ul id="UL_CEA4CD427612471CA3540AD5430B21C2" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_B007BBFF5E5743C89A24651737F64808" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Go to COLD SDS and disconnect the Service jumper.
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">A pair of scissors 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> See : 
<xref href="http://localhost:20347/tsm?tsm=TSM000376EN.US&amp;pageid=GUID-1C874C66-3A17-4AC4-886B-753A1A37D196.xml" scope="external" format="html" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>02 Open the ink system</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the rear top cover of the ink system.
</p><p class="- topic/p "> See : 
<xref href="http://localhost:20347/tsm?tsm=TSM000376EN.US&amp;pageid=GUID-44A21941-A21F-4C37-A066-3CEA7BE54DAA.xml" scope="external" format="html" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>02 How to remove the rear top cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the pump tube.
</p><p class="- topic/p "> See:<xref href="http://localhost:20347/tsm?tsm=TSM000376EN.US&amp;pageid=GUID-17BE5A1E-1F83-432B-A7C3-6E2D5D312EEC.xml" scope="external" format="html" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>02 How to remove the pump tube of the ink pump</xref> 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-D14B60A0-8F57-4875-8B22-7D150696F8D7" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-2D7D94A0-B26C-4C0B-B6A3-20C8621663A2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-63E079CC-61F0-4AF7-80FE-0189DD0FDD73" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-5DEA8606-9D2F-4152-A47A-378846D78EE1" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-7D1F04DA-2BDE-4129-87F4-602CE89C5001-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7D1F04DA-2BDE-4129-87F4-602CE89C5001-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-5EA27C95-5182-4D96-BE42-E409FBB87504" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> Procedure</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-C5035010-056F-494D-A2DC-E59ECE77F797" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 2-wheel rotor.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-53FE3B29-AD89-4814-9590-C9BD22918D7E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-873B33A4-63D2-4DBB-A72B-28747413546C-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-873B33A4-63D2-4DBB-A72B-28747413546C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install the 4-wheel rotor.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-4A270ABC-1936-4F42-A771-4B0BDED43DEE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E7B36BB7-99EB-410F-9100-59AEE1D2DA3E-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E7B36BB7-99EB-410F-9100-59AEE1D2DA3E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><note id="GUID-6AF9DECE-BFFD-4862-9D08-190EC8B63E96" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The rollers are detachable from the holder. You can combine parts from two rotors to create one 4-roller rotor for use in another pump.
</p><fig id="GUID-C3FD113E-0C60-4E88-8047-C36EE7CD2860" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-394DB057-240E-4060-80BD-843A7511F0F7-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-394DB057-240E-4060-80BD-843A7511F0F7-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Register Modification 50 in SDS and on the modification sticker.</b>
</p></note></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-B389A763-3BDF-47D8-8530-E2CB730B7104.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
